  "detailed_description": "A war chess game that you build random characters, skills and weapon combinations, and raid random levels!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/55df17c57d360540af67a20e7af8fd83.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/55df17c57d360540af67a20e7af8fd83.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/55df17c57d360540af67a20e7af8fd83.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Characters: More than a dozen heroes with very different combat performance and fighting styles, each with their own strengths, waiting for you to choose and unlock!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a187bcc019dba6bbc99e24362660ecaf.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a187bcc019dba6bbc99e24362660ecaf.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a187bcc019dba6bbc99e24362660ecaf.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/6cb52f5199c8385b3a82334ec4d80a4a.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/6cb52f5199c8385b3a82334ec4d80a4a.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/6cb52f5199c8385b3a82334ec4d80a4a.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Weapons: Hundreds of weapons are waiting to be unlocked and collected. <br>With different weapons in hand, character’s attack range, skills and attack animations may change accordingly. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/606f78751fe0d416639f2effffa93e1a.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/606f78751fe0d416639f2effffa93e1a.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/606f78751fe0d416639f2effffa93e1a.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a9cca2a3bde0b0080eceb714ddcf2b0e.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a9cca2a3bde0b0080eceb714ddcf2b0e.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a9cca2a3bde0b0080eceb714ddcf2b0e.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/f56b6c4a714dbd27375cc248e77338d4.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/f56b6c4a714dbd27375cc248e77338d4.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/f56b6c4a714dbd27375cc248e77338d4.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Skills: Skill effects are diverse and the performance is gorgeous. Hundreds of skill combinations are available, and the must-kill skill can change the character's combat positioning, bringing a brand new game experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/49c2dc5d92a2737121a4351a1e74b941.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/49c2dc5d92a2737121a4351a1e74b941.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/49c2dc5d92a2737121a4351a1e74b941.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Simple operation. Under the premise of retaining the core gameplay of randomly constructed combinations, the game supports acceleration and automatic skill releasing, making it easy to control the pace.<br>The playability has been verified by tens of thousands of players with hundreds of hours of average play time, and the war chess is re-optimized and adjusted based on the core gameplay, providing you with more abundant game content and more interesting game experience.",
  "about_the_game": "A war chess game that you build random characters, skills and weapon combinations, and raid random levels!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/55df17c57d360540af67a20e7af8fd83.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/55df17c57d360540af67a20e7af8fd83.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/55df17c57d360540af67a20e7af8fd83.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Characters: More than a dozen heroes with very different combat performance and fighting styles, each with their own strengths, waiting for you to choose and unlock!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a187bcc019dba6bbc99e24362660ecaf.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a187bcc019dba6bbc99e24362660ecaf.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/a187bcc019dba6bbc99e24362660ecaf.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/6cb52f5199c8385b3a82334ec4d80a4a.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/6cb52f5199c8385b3a82334ec4d80a4a.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"htt