5584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/f56b6c4a714dbd27375cc248e77338d4.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Skills: Skill effects are diverse and the performance is gorgeous. Hundreds of skill combinations are available, and the must-kill skill can change the character's combat positioning, bringing a brand new game experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/49c2dc5d92a2737121a4351a1e74b941.poster.avif?t=1715584885\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/49c2dc5d92a2737121a4351a1e74b941.webm?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863050/extras/49c2dc5d92a2737121a4351a1e74b941.mp4?t=1715584885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Simple operation. Under the premise of retaining the core gameplay of randomly constructed combinations, the game supports acceleration and automatic skill releasing, making it easy to control the pace.<br>The playability has been verified by tens of thousands of players with hundreds of hours of average play time, and the war chess is re-optimized and adjusted based on the core gameplay, providing you with more abundant game content and more interesting game experience.",
